    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Problem"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The customer is using Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 on-premise and had severe issues with their existing mobility solution. It had a limited feature set and lacked some essential attributes needed by any enterprise app. They readily shifted to Folio3 mobility suite to be used by their workforce into the following areas:"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Timesheets"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Approval"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Procurement"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The mobility suite consists of native mobile apps for iOS and Android and the responsive Web portal applications and middleware for each area. The customer had the following infrastructure and DevOps needs:"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The web portals and middleware apps to be hosted in Azure"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Azure single sign-on for mobile apps and web portals"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Mobile apps build distribution"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Apps connecting with Dynamics AX 2012 hosted on-premise"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Infrastructure security & Apps monitoring"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Disaster recovery"
        }
      ],
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Problem"
        },
